_______________________________________________________________________________
"Damage Absorption"   
        The idea of this power is it allows the psionicist to alter his
        own aura to absorb kinetic energy.  The power adds about 100 
        hit points which will fade over time, very quickly at low guild
        levels but slower and slower as guild level rises.  Until this
        power wears off, both wounds and healing will affect these
        'temporary' hit points first.  However, the gradual loss
        of hit points will never cause you to go below the number you
        had when you invoked the power (damage from other sources WILL).
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  3		Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  absorption
